## Module Access UX

- Left sidebar: sections with enabled/total counters.
- Search is global across all sections; filters apply only within the selected section when search is empty.
- While search is active, filter chips are disabled so search and filters do not interfere.
- Clicking a left section or a top filter resets scroll so the module list starts under the sticky toolbar.
