- Use a two-level master-detail flow: compact module cards first, then a dedicated full-width rights screen for one selected module.
- Do not expand permission matrices inline inside the module list.
- The module detail screen has a prominent leading Back action in the sticky top toolbar, its own rights search, presets, one category accordion open at a time, and independent Access/View/Edit columns.
- Warning state when module is on but no rights granted (`–¢—Ä–µ–±—É—é—Ç—Å—è –ø—Ä–∞–≤–∞`).
